    <div class="container7p2q">
        <section class="section5r8t" id="services3x8m">
            <h2>Our Comprehensive Gutter Services</h2>
            <p>At AuroviHub, we specialize in providing complete gutter solutions that protect your property from water damage and ensure optimal drainage performance throughout all seasons. Our experienced technicians utilize advanced techniques and quality materials to deliver exceptional results. <a href="#contact8p2m" class="btn2m7k">Click here to continue</a> and discover how we can help maintain your gutter system.</p>
            
            <div class="grid3x9w">
                <div class="card6h4n">
                    <h4>Gutter Cleaning Services</h4>
                    <p>Our thorough cleaning process removes leaves, debris, pine needles, and accumulated sediment from your gutters and downspouts. We ensure complete water flow restoration and inspect for potential issues during every cleaning session. Regular maintenance prevents overflow, foundation damage, and landscape erosion.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card6h4n">
                    <h4>Gutter Repair Solutions</h4>
                    <p>We fix leaking seams, replace damaged sections, reattach loose gutters, and repair sagging areas. Our repair services address rust spots, hole patching, and bracket reinforcement. Every repair is completed with attention to detail ensuring long-lasting performance and structural integrity.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card6h4n">
                    <h4>Downspout Management</h4>
                    <p>Proper downspout function is critical for effective water diversion. We unclog blocked downspouts, extend drainage away from foundations, install underground drainage systems, and ensure proper water discharge. Our downspout services prevent basement flooding and foundation deterioration.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card6h4n">
                    <h4>Gutter Guard Installation</h4>
                    <p>Reduce maintenance frequency with our gutter guard systems. We install various protection types including mesh screens, foam inserts, and surface tension guards. These systems minimize debris accumulation while maintaining optimal water flow and reducing cleaning requirements.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card6h4n">
                    <h4>Seasonal Inspections</h4>
                    <p>Our comprehensive inspection service identifies potential problems before they become costly repairs. We examine gutter alignment, check for corrosion, assess bracket stability, and evaluate overall system performance. Seasonal inspections extend gutter lifespan and prevent emergency situations.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card6h4n">
                    <h4>Emergency Gutter Services</h4>
                    <p>When unexpected gutter failures occur, our emergency response team provides rapid assistance. We handle storm damage, sudden leaks, detached sections, and overflow situations. Quick response prevents additional property damage and restores protection immediately.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
